# First faculty aftermath after defeating Marius Thaule.

[header]
id|first_faculty_aftermath

[steps]
say|Marius Thaule|Enough.;You did not come here;for a routine student exercise.;Bart Iver sent you.
say|Marius Thaule|Then hear me clearly.;He was removed because he would not stop.;Not because he was easy to ignore.
say|Marius Thaule|Still, you beat every assistant I set before you.;Then you beat me.;That earns you this.
badge|Foundations Badge
flag|got_foundations_badge
say|Marius Thaule|The Foundations Badge is more than a trophy.;It opens doors this faculty keeps shut.
say|Marius Thaule|There is one more thing.;A sealed index page from Bart Iver's confiscated Concordance.
item|8|1
flag|received_concordance_index
say|Marius Thaule|I was ordered to keep it from him.;Now I am placing that choice on you instead.
say|Marius Thaule|If you carry it back to Bart,;do it knowing this was never harmless.
flag|first_faculty_aftermath_done
